    "body": "Currently docker images don't benefit from layer caching for the dependencies installed through the package manager, since files from the spack folder are copied over in the step before that.\r\n\r\nThis PR should make building docker images faster when cache is available, and should reduce the download size when a new version is available in the registry.",
